 ALL_D0_Overview {
  m_sTitle "Overview"
  m_sTextData "TotallyChernarussian™ SF conduct an air assault on a rocky island in the Green Sea, which was previously occupied by Russian forces."\
  ""\
  "Heavily inspired by real events which took place in Minecraine."
  m_bEmptyFactionVisibility 1
 }
 CDF_D1_Situation {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "I. Situation"
  m_sTextData "May 8th, 2022."\
  "You are Chernarussian SF, tasked with liberating an island in the Green Sea that was previously occupied by Russian forces."\
  ""\
  "In preparation of an assault, the island was taken under significant fire over the past weeks, including the destruction of most air defense by a TB2 drone."\
  "Yesterday, two Su-27 conducted a bombing run on the building group near the former lighthouse, severely damaging multiple houses."\
  ""\
  "The amount of enemy forces on the island is estimated to be around 30."\
  "Their only remaining air defense capability is:"\
  "- A small supply of MANPADS"\
  "- Possibly, a ZU-23-2 in the north-eastern settlement may remain operational due to a close miss, but will be unable to engage any low flying aircraft due to its position, with the exception of aircraft south to south-east of the settement."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_CDF"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 CDF_D2_Mission {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "II. Mission"
  m_sTextData "Gain a decisive advantage by taking full control of both major building groups."\
  ""\
  "Alternatively, destroy a signficiant amount of enemy forces and extract."\
  ""\
  "If heavy casualties are taken, organize a withdrawal from the island."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_CDF"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 CDF_D3_Execution {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "III. Execution"
  m_sTextData "Commanders discretion."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_CDF"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 CDF_D4_Support {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "IV. Service / Support"
  m_sTextData "a. Service"\
  ""\
  "None for infantry"\
  "No repair/resupply for helicopters"\
  ""\
  "b. Support"\
  ""\
  "Mi-24, two Mi-8. The Mi-24 has 40 rockets, each Mi-8 has 90 rockets."\
  "Troops are already loaded in the Mi-8s, with 1+2 being in Salacia."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_CDF"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 CDF_D5_Signal {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "V. Command / Signal"
  m_sTextData "Callsigns:"\
  ""\
  "0 - Platoon HQ"\
  "1 - 1st Team"\
  "2 - 2nd Team"\
  "3 - 3rd Team"\
  ""\
  "Neptune - Mi-24"\
  "Salacia - 1st Mi-8"\
  "Venilia - 2nd Mi-8"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_CDF"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
 ALL_D6_Notes {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "Notes"
  m_sTextData "Setup Timer (CDF): 4 minutes"\
  ""\
  "CDF start about 4km north of the island, so it will be directly south."\
  "Available airspace around the island is 4km north, and 3km south/west/east."\
  ""\
  "IMPORTANT NOTE FOR HELI CREW: Due to a current issue with WCS and in-vehicle-spawning, you need to leave and re-enter your seat, otherwise you will not be able to use flares (Shift+F) or rockets!"\
  ""\
  "IGLA TUTORIAL: Keep the target behind the reticle while holding LCTRL for a few seconds. Once you get a lock tone, you are clear to fire."\
  ""\
  "End Conditions:"\
  "- CDF Major Victory: RU lost control of both objectives"\
  "- CDF Minor Victory: CDF extracted after >60% RU player+AI casualties"\
  "- CDF Minor Defeat: CDF extracted after 50-80% CDF casualties"\
  "- CDF Major Defeat: >80% CDF casualties"\
  "CDF will receive info messages when the conditions for minor outcomes are reached."
  m_bShowForAnyFaction 1
  m_iOrder 6
 }
 RU_D1_Situation {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "I. Situation"
  m_sTextData "May 8th, 2022."\
  "As part of the Russian invasion of TotallyChernarus™, your platoon is occupying a rocky island in the Green Sea."\
  ""\
  "Over the recent weeks, the island has come under increasingly frequent Chernarussian fire, including the destruction of most air defense by a TB2 drone."\
  "Yesterday, two Su-27 conducted a bombing run on the building group near the former lighthouse, significantly damaging multiple houses."\
  ""\
  "a. Enemy Forces"\
  ""\
  "Just now, three helicopters including an Mi-24 were sighted to the North of the island. It is possible that an enemy assault is imminent."\
  ""\
  "b. Friendly Forces"\
  ""\
  "The amount of friendly forces on the island is around 30. 1st squad is currently located at the central-western building group while 2nd squad is at the north-eastern settlement."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_AFRF"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 RU_D2_Mission {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "II. Mission"
  m_sTextData "Defend the island."\
  ""\
  "It is important that the enemy does not gain control over both major building groups, as this would give them a decisive advantage."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_AFRF"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 RU_D3_Execution {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "III. Execution"
  m_sTextData "Determined by the squad leaders."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_AFRF"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 RU_D4_Support {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "IV. Service / Support"
  m_sTextData "a. Service"\
  ""\
  "Each squad has a crate with one Igla launcher."\
  "One additional launcher was lost, it is likely either stored in the underground shelter at 04 02, was taken to the windmill in the south west, or remained somewhere around the harbor."\
  ""\
  "b. Support"\
  ""\
  "One of the ZU-23-2, located in the middle of the north-eastern settlement, was not destroyed by the recent TB2 strikes due to a close miss and remains operational."\
  "However, nearby buildings mostly block visibility on low flying targets."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_AFRF"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
